{"tid":1618762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙面法唔係文宣重點啊喂！緊急法=法治已亡","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:14:47.000Z","uid":27534,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0f621c6e115bdf723048cf99365516ca57908ecf","tid":1618762,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"［蒙面法］大家討論嘅焦點錯哂<br />\n一邊有人講蒙面法會影響和理非出嚟，對場運動不利。一邊講歡迎Winter on Fire 序幕。<br />\n<br />\n但真正重要嘅唔係蒙面法，<br />\n係引用緊急法。<br />\n<br />\n明顯今次蒙面法只係個幌子，為引用緊急法試水溫；緊急法繞過所有立法程序，毫無法理上嘅制衡，以「行政」完全凌駕「立法」，係「三權分立」遭破壞嘅鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n文宣戰：<br />\n引用緊急法 = 法治已亡。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔洗入去同佢討論蒙面的自由與正當<br />\n我哋一嘢屌佢 「緊急法，破壞法治」<br />\n將個agenda set返做政府做錯事（而不是去解釋蒙面沒有錯）<br />\n<br />\n重覆：唔好俾佢帶風向傾蒙面法嘅正當性。<br />\n<br />\n全力反對引用緊急法破壞法治！<br />\n<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9daccf38610f483df41bb08e41c033ea37ae51","tid":1618762,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a7888fb7782d060992f62bfdc78618d16a6eda","tid":1618762,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵貴神速 今晚就要先聲奪人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4adc1dccb12c198974eec97320b2ad42e3ea8d6c","tid":1618762,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"仲有議會都係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔再需要議員立法，再有人講血債票償，全部都係共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4483e445fdc23b854d163843a065c79e9238caa","tid":1618762,"uid":112103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975fd0a18bfa391417b80d94e8174ac8944ff569","tid":1618762,"uid":210121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"緊急法=無限權力。到時一切都可禁止。"},{"pid":"703808d4992c3a910c0422561fb6430e77f7b2ab","tid":1618762,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"唔好再講緊急法，全部人講獨裁法<br />\n<br />\n緊急法嗰名好似好中性無奈，實制係行獨裁，林鄭想點都得，直接決定落實<br />\n<br />\n警察濫權濫捕？林鄭直接獨裁法授權<br />\n做文宣，貼連儂牆？獨裁法列刑事<br />\nFacebok twitter文宣？獨裁法禁假新聞，由政府定義真假<br />\n<br />\n獨裁法係黐線的，幫手宣傳一下，今日之內要正名"},{"pid":"f6c6d580f532bd234231cea29faf782b1aaea895","tid":1618762,"uid":27534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"佢岀得緊急法即係呼籲我地攬炒！"},{"pid":"ca9bc4f77ea48a1a6128291453b1b7edef1e7761","tid":1618762,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dcc276a357acb496aeb48bc18314d20e04554f","tid":1618762,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a00438ea831469d6e08d09a0c5ae995ff3d7a2d","tid":1618762,"uid":193328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"平時行之有效的法例又不用<br />\n<br />\n成日講平時行之有效嘅法例<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你整得緊急法 即是平時嘅法例唔係行之有效<br />\n<br />\n咁獨立調查委員會一樣可以整，點解唔整？  好嬲，係搞就公平d，我唔係嬲蒙面法，我係嬲點解呢個香港咁唔公平"},{"pid":"6e9d157881220ef2616398db690bfaa12a169942","tid":1618762,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfcfb860abdfde6e1704612cef8070875546753","tid":1618762,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7723f81c9db96bdf9a7a6c3069f1cdde92275f5f","tid":1618762,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"推 緊急法先係重點"},{"pid":"58824c4e470b6542a0bc32640ca87e69662c63bd","tid":1618762,"uid":205241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2be585e34f953455746d33eabc8632838d1fd64a","tid":1618762,"uid":205241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"緊急法根本就直接破壞左香港三權分立呢個咁重要嘅核心價值<br />\n亦同時開左先例比其他政府想推行嘅法例<br />\n香港堂堂一個法治之都 法治社會<br />\n一於煲大佢 令全部人都明白推蒙面法所衍生嘅嚴重性"},{"pid":"70cf951955855d5cab8b3442d12fd73b7b647332","tid":1618762,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二百幾萬<strong>和理非</strong> 係時候一齊出手</span><br />\n<br />\n銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非加入 戰況大增千倍的</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新戰術</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}